description:

https://phit.click/freecourse

 

I take you through how I went from weighing 250lbs and having no faith in myself. I had to LEARN and EARN my belief I could lose 100lbs and then build my self-esteem along the way. I detail what I did and how you can do the same no matter how much weight you have to lose.
